法蘭琪 
Frankie...

376
00:44:31,450 --> 00:44:34,880
你父親很久以前就死了
your father died long ago.

377
00:44:36,840 --> 00:44:38,670
不管我是什么 
Whatever I am, I've...

378
00:44:39,590 --> 00:44:41,880
我以前也死過 沒那么糟
I've died before. This isn't so bad.

379
00:44:41,970 --> 00:44:44,260
我才剛找到你 我不想再失去你
I just found you. I don't want to lose you again.

380
00:44:44,380 --> 00:44:48,890
沒關系
Hey... it's okay.

381
00:44:53,020 --> 00:44:56,520
