I got to live every parent's greatest dream.

382
00:45:03,490 --> 00:45:07,530
我看見我的孩子長大了
I got to see my child grow up.

383
00:45:12,910 --> 00:45:14,250
我愛你 爸
I love you, Dad.

384
00:45:20,710 --> 00:45:22,090
我愛你 小餅干
I love you, Cookie.

385
